race.description: Phil Mclennan Earthmoving Max 150 Points Final
race.comment: HAALAND (1) flew the lids from out wide with an impressive turn of foot, going on to clock 20.17 when a 2.5 lengths winner over 350m at this track last time. Will go close again if runs up to latest. LOVE THIS BAR (2) recorded his Best Time this course and distance last time when a 20.00 winner of a Grade 5 in the quickest time on the card. In form and must include in calculations. REEL 'EM SISSY (8) clocked a new course and distance PB last time, finishing a 2.25 lengths second behind LOVE THIS BAR in 20.17. Has the ability and can measure up. GEORGIAN DAISY (3) won last start after racing on the pace. Sure to run well again.
